"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:10.5.2\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">10.5.2</span> 標題：手鐲、臂鐲、腳鐲（bracelet, armlet, anklet）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： אֶצְעָדָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ’ets‘adah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:50\">NUM 31:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam1:10\">2SA 1:10</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： עֶכֶס</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ‘ekes)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:18\">ISA 3:18</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： צָמִיד</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： tsamid)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:22\">GEN 24:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:30\">GEN 24:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:47\">GEN 24:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:50\">NUM 31:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:11\">EZK 16:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek23:42\">EZK 23:42</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： צְעָדָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ts‘adah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:20\">ISA 3:20</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： χλιδών</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： chlidōn)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt10:4\">JDT 10:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir21:21\">SIR 21:21</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： ψέλιον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： pselion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt10:4\">JDT 10:4</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0532_bracelets_gold.jpg\" alt=\"以羚羊頭裝飾的手鐲\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">以羚羊頭裝飾的手鐲 (Walters Art Museum, Public domain, CC BY-SA 3.0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>手鐲／臂鐲是戴在手腕／手臂上的一種首飾，為圓形，用金屬做成。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>手鐲戴在手腕上，而臂鐲通常佩戴在肘部以上。如果必須要區分手臂的各個部分，希伯來文<em>tsamid</em> 在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:11\">EZK 16:11</a> 中可以翻譯為「手腕上的鐲子」。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:50\">NUM 31:50</a> ：如果沒有不同的詞來區分戴在手腕上的環和戴在上臂的環，那麼在這節經文中，可以使用一個集合名詞，例如，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 譯為「珠寶」（“jewelry”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> ）。</p>\n<p>翻譯者必須注意，不要使用表示戴在手臂上面但不是用金屬做成物件的詞語。例如，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam1:10\">2SA 1:10</a> 中譯為“arm-band”（「臂帶」），但在現代英文中，人們可能會誤以為這是布料或塑料做成的袖章。</p>\n<p>關於希伯來文<em>‘ekes</em> 和<em>ts‘adah</em> ，參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">10.5 珠寶、首飾、飾物 (jewelry, ornaments)&lt;REALIA:10.5&gt;</a> 就<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:18-Isa3:23\">ISA 3:18–ISA 3:23</a> 所做的討論。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt10:4\">JDT 10:4</a> 中，希臘文<em>chlidōn</em> 和<em>pselion</em> 都可以既指（戴在手臂上的）「手鐲」，又指（戴在腳上的）「腳鐲」。如果目標語言有分別表示「手鐲」和「腳鐲」的詞語，那麼本節經文可以同時使用這兩個詞；或者也可以說，「戴在手腕和腳踝上的金屬飾帶。」</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
